spirit:vendorExtensions.actel-cc:description: The CoreAHBLite component implements a multi-master AHB-Lite bus. It provides up to 4 AHB-Lite master interfaces, and up to 16 AHB-Lite slave interfaces. It is possible to allocate one or more slave slots to a "combined region" that is accessed through a further slave interface. Slave slots allocated to the combined region are not available for separate connection.
